title: Aiseesoft.FoneLab.8.3.26+patch
description:
Recover the Lost Data from Your Broken iPhone/iPad/ iPod touch
If your device is locked because of a lost or forgotten password, or it got smashed, dropped into water, damaged, or even broken, no need to fret. All is not lost! If your device has ever been successfully connected with iTunes, it's possible to get back the lost data from the broken device directly without backup. If you have backups in iTunes or iCloud, you can also recover lost data from iTunes or iCloud backup. To help you rescue the data on your iPhone, iPad or iPod touch which suffers from situations mentioned above, this iPhone Data Recovery will provide the best way to recover lost contacts, photos, text messages, WhatsApp, iMessages, videos/music, call history, notes, etc. from your broken device
